        <mxCell id="-CRQHxzJXNvNzKxAn57p-96" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 21px; text-indent: -21px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot; style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;0. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot; style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Все системы общаются через API Gareway.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot; style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt; Не все взаимодействия отображены ввиде стрелок, чтобы не перегружать диаграмму.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 21px; text-indent: -21px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot; style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 21px; text-indent: -21px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot; style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Инициировать платёж&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;YS Text&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;—&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;т&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;орговая площадка инициирует платёж, отправив необходимые данные (ID пользователя, ID заказа, сумма заказа) в платёжный сервис.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 21px; text-indent: -21px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot; style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;2.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Предоставить статус платежа&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;YS Text&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;— п&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;латё&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;жный сервис принял запрос на проведение оплаты,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot; class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;подтвердил возможность проведения платежа со счёта клиента, назначил идентификатор для этой транзакции и установил статус.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 21px; text-indent: -21px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot; style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;3.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Подтверждение платежа&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;YS Text&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;— т&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;орговая площадка уведомляет платёжный сервис о подтверждении операции, отправляя ID транзакции.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 21px; text-indent: -21px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot; style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;4.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Запросить статус платежа&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;YS Text&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;— т&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;орговая площадка отправляет запрос в платёжный сервис для получения текущего статуса обработки транзакции по ID.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 21px; text-indent: -21px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot; style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;5.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Подтверждение отмены платежа (альтернативный сценарий)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;YS Text&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;— п&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;латёжный сервис уведомляет систему об успешной отмене платежа, предоставляя статус отменённой транзакции.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 21px; text-indent: -21px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(255, 51, 51), rgb(255, 51, 51)); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot; class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;6. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(255, 51, 51), rgb(255, 51, 51));&quot;&gt;Регистрация, авторизация, аутентикация&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: initial; font-family: &amp;quot;YS Text&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;— &lt;/span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-family: &amp;quot;YS Text&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;вся работа с токенами идёт напрямую с системой для работы с пользователями&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 21px; text-indent: -21px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-family: &amp;quot;YS Text&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot; class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;7.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot;&gt;Редактирование профиля пользователя&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;— все данные о пользователе и их редактирование доступно через систему для работы с пользователями после аутентикации.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 21px; text-indent: -21px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-family: &amp;quot;YS Text&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot; class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;8.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot;&gt;Нотификации&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;— система AuctionFlow отправляет нотификации об изменениях в статусах товаров, услуг, аукционов и платежей.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 21px; text-indent: -21px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-family: &amp;quot;YS Text&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-size: 15px; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot; class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;9.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot;&gt;Создание и редактирование товаров, услуг, заказов&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;— все операции редактирования и просмотра товаров, услуг, аукционов, заявок идут через систему AuctionFlow&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 21px; text-indent: -21px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-family: &amp;quot;YS Text&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-size: 15px; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot; class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;10.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot;&gt;Валидация токена, получение данных профиля&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;— система&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;YS Text&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;AuctionFlow валидирует данные о пользователе через систему работы с пользователем.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 21px; text-indent: -21px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-family: &amp;quot;YS Text&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-size: 15px; font-kerning: auto; font-opti